title: History of Birdperson: Rick and Morty Timeline

media:group.media:title: History of Birdperson: Rick and Morty Timeline
media:group.media:description:
In this video we look at the timeline of Birdperson from Rick and Morty. Created by Justin Roiland, we look at life and history of Birdperson. His friendship with Rick, meeting Tammy and Birdperson's daughter. With Rick and Morty season 6 out on Adult Swim, I thought it was the best time to look at the history of Rick and Morty characters.

Rick and Morty is an American adult animated science fiction sitcom created by Justin Roiland and Dan Harmon for Cartoon Network's Adult Swim. The series follows the misadventures of cynical mad scientist Rick Sanchez and his grandson Morty Smith.
